The plan outlook is simple:

Position myself well enough to sit in coins that are diverse in each sector (memes, RWA, launchpads, CCM etc) to make greater lengths as they shake out tourists (that crashout every week) thru Q4. 

I've made most of my successful trades being late-early and allocated to coins/ideas that have established themselves enough with a core foundation to achieve their mission. Sometimes it doesn't work out, which is completely fine - nobody has a 100% W/R (I sure as hell don't lmaeon).

But what if I am right and it hits? That's the thrill of trading. Manage your own risk as mine =/ yours.

Some say it's luck (maybe it is), luck = a skill. Anyone can paint the vision, but can you execute well enough?

Zoom out, the future is bright - I won't explain further.

Let's win.
